    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1901-10-09T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1901-10-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="50"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d50">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Infante</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Adee</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Chile</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-10-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 9, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. Secretary</hi>: I am in receipt of instructions from
                    the Government of Chile directing me to take such steps as may be required to
                    obtain for the commander and officers of the training ship <hi rend="italic"
                        >General <pb facs="0116" n="36" xml:id="pg_36"/> Baquedano</hi>, at present
                    anchored in the bay of New York, permission to deposit in the Washington
                    Monument, on behalf of the people of Chile, a plaque commemorative of that
                    illustrious leader of the American independence and founder of the Republic of
                    the United States of America.</p>
                <p>I shall be thankful if your excellency will kindly apply to appropriate
                    authorities for the permission to place the said plaque, provided there should
                    be no objection on your part.</p>
                <p>It is for me a pleasure, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">E. Infante.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
